{"description":"In https://github.com/SonarSource/sonar-java/blob/master/java-squid/src/main/java/org/sonar/java/ast/visitors/FileLinesVisitor.java : for multi-line comments, only the line of the first token is counted.\n\nFor instance:\n\n{code}\nclass foo {\n  /*\n   * This is a comment\n   */\n}\n{code}\n\n, will return \"1\u003d0,2\u003d1,3\u003d0,4\u003d0,5\u003d0\".","component":"SonarJava","component_version":"1.4"}